               <typeofhazard class="+ topic/li hazard-d/typeofhazard ">SYSTEM OPERATION LOCKED</typeofhazard>
               <howtoavoid class="+ topic/li hazard-d/howtoavoid ">In forced inverter operation there is no automatic switch
over to bypass operation if the rectifier output and battery are unavailable.</howtoavoid>
            </messagepanel>
         </hazardstatement>
         <note conref="P_How_to_Change_to_Forced_Static_Switch_Operation_TSK_DD00581156.dita#HowToChangeToForcedStaticSwitchOper-7413AC65/ThisModeIsATemporaryModeAndShouldNo-8695221D"
